OL,3,CReform UK councillor defects to Tories
OL,4,Cafter bullying and sexism claims
OL,6,FA Staffordshire county councillor has
OL,7,Fdefected from Reform UK to the
OL,8,FConservative Party, citing allegations
OL,9,Fof bullying and sexism within the
OL,10,FReform group.
OL,12,FCharlotte Kelly, who represents Leek
OL,13,FRural on Staffordshire County Council,
OL,14,Fsaid she could no longer remain with
OL,15,FReform UK, after what she described as
OL,16,F"a period of reflection" on her
OL,17,Fpolitical future.
OL,26,@xD@AOUxD@XO]
