OL,3,CReform UK councillor defects to Tories
OL,4,Cafter bullying and sexism claims
OL,6,FIn a statement announcing the move, Ms
OL,7,FKelly said she had experienced
OL,8,F"bullying and sexism on a regular
OL,9,Fbasis" while a member of the Reform
OL,10,Fgroup.
OL,12,FShe claimed the party's leadership had
OL,13,Fbeen unwilling to deal with the issue,
OL,14,Fmaking it "impossible" for her to
OL,15,Fcontinue as part of the group.
OL,17,FMs Kelly said Conservative councillors
OL,18,Fhad been "welcoming, supportive and
OL,19,Frespectful" during that time.
OL,26,@pD@AOUqD@FO]vD@KOUvD@VO]zD@JOU{D@KO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1781093477
OL,3,CReform UK councillor defects to Tories
OL,4,Cafter bullying and sexism claims
OL,6,FA former Conservative member, she said
OL,7,Fshe felt the party under leader Kemi
OL,8,FBadenoch was now her "natural home".
OL,10,F"This decision is about ensuring I can
OL,11,Fcontinue to represent the people of
OL,12,FLeek Rural effectively and
OL,13,Fpositively," she said.
OL,15,F"My focus remains on delivering for
OL,16,Fresidents and standing up for the
OL,17,Fcommunities I was elected to serve."
OL,26,@pD@VOUpD@cO]rD@AOUuD@LO]wD@AOUyD@dO]
