OL,3,CReform UK councillor defects to Tories
OL,4,Cafter bullying and sexism claims
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FConservative group leader Philip White
OL,12,Fwelcomed Ms Kelly's decision to join
OL,13,Fthe party.
OL,15,FHe described her as a "dedicated and
OL,16,Fhardworking councillor" and said her
OL,17,F"experience, local knowledge and
OL,18,Fcommitment to Leek Rural" would make
OL,19,Fher "a valuable member" of the
OL,20,FConservative group.
OL,26,@wD@WOUxD@WO]yD@AOUzD@YO]{D@EOU{D@WO]
