OL,3,CReform UK councillor defects to Tories
OL,4,Cafter bullying and sexism claims
OL,6,FMr White also said the Conservatives
OL,7,Fwould offer confidential support to
OL,8,Fany other Reform UK councillors on the
OL,9,Fcounty council who may be experiencing
OL,10,Fdifficulties.
OL,12,FMs Kelly will join the Conservative
OL,13,Fgroup on Staffordshire County Council
OL,14,Fwith immediate effect.
OL,16,FReform UK has been approached for
OL,17,Fcomment.
